Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku, who became a subordinate of Doma, came to get Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because of the appearance of the Claw of Hermos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai disappeared before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The message left by Pegasus revealed the truth about Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With such a mighty enemy ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} and Kaiba, who were chosen by the Legendary Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The three of us have to join forces no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:02:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Target is the Nameless Pharaoh"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! There's no way this can happen in reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it! There's a strong power coming from the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three cards are resonating towards one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it became our destiny to defeat Doma ever since we got these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny? Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decide the path I follow on {\i1}my{\i0} road of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak words like "destiny" or "fate" in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that {\i1}now{\i0}, Kaiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't opponents you can beat by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take orders from {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle things with Doma by {\i1}myself{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you can continue playing your make-believe occult games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mokuba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to rely on someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a card like Claw of Hermos, we aren't gonna be beaten by the likes of Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming more like yourself now, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep being so pessimistic, nothing will get resolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're {\i1}they{\i0} the only ones gettin' such strong cards? It's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to keep searching...! They must be somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses... My glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're right there, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus is missing and we have no further clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that we need to go after those Doma bastards and get Mai back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that, we have no idea where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, why don't you guys come over to my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Professor Hopkins..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Professor Hopkins, he may have some clues on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor returned to America to unveil the mysteries of those relics found underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma and the relics...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that the both of them must be related to one another in some ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've already decided, all we need is to find a way to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY!! Let {\i1}us{\i0} get on, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat, he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use my car to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at how many people we have here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we also...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what are two here for anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our fate in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Yugi an' his gang somehow obtained super strong cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the two of us got nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is just starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that Professor Hopkins is an avid card mania collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have many of those collector's must-have cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still room for our skills ta' improve, long as we get hold a' rare cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, Mai Kujaku has gotten {\i1}really{\i0} strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pass it over. Let {\i1}me{\i0} look at it for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I{\i0} am the navigator now, so don't interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be faster if we took this road instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will going to Alaska do us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have {\i1}any{\i0} sense of direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? Where are we again? Somewhere around here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With my own will, I've chosen to fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things you guys obtained in Battle City...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to catch up to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to beat you all, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't convince her with my words now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're mistaken, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the way we aim to become True Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must not be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Mai has been\N bought over by our enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And even Pegasus's soul has been taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've lost too many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We couldn't get Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} to cooperate with us either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like it will be a tough fight ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stop me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continued with the fight, I would have defeated Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you hadn't interfered!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shard of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Release your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you suppose is the reason Varon's in this state right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't have anything to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the retribution from interrupting my Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interrupt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already {\i1}lost{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anymore, Rafael...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you off easily if you continue spouting rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up 'till now, how have you been perceiving that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Dragon card that appeared in his deck suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is something only the Chosen True Duelists can obtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not think lightly of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Jounouchi is a {\i1}True Duelist{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll {\i1}show{\i0} you who the {\i1}real{\i0} True Duelist around here is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! My bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi, I won't let this matter rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make up for Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat Jounouchi!...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, we have to deal with Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to Duel with {\i1}him{\i0} all of a sudden now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that he has received the Legendary Dragon card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the situation is still in our favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we defeat the nameless Pharaoh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of them will be easy pickings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to lure Yugi out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know where they are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already made preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down, boy! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I bought a little too much food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's rather heavy, but please keep going a bit longer, Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitors..?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Billy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins! Rebeca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, he...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have done such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be Doma! They're the only ones capable of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they want to capture Professor Hopkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there was a relation with those cipher texts after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, that fragment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the crystal-like fragment I left with the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right... It's all right. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa told me to hold on to this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end we don't even know what this thing is and we don't have any clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we {\i1}do{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crime if I've ever seen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, my grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's not jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets observe what the enemy does first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end we can only wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, shouldn't we eat something first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't eaten all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, can I borrow your kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Otogi, you know how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm sure Professor Hopkins will return to us safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda, please set the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jounouchi, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Haga and Ryuzaki run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, Yugi and Rebeca aren't here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can there be any cards here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there was, they'd 'ov been burnt anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like eating takoyaki...\N {\i1}[Fried/baked octopus dumplings]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna eat spaghetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat sushi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, please save my grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. I promise I'll rescue the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know know to say this, so I kept quiet about it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nameless Pharaoh, I'll wait for you at Death Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must come alone. The Three Musketeers of Doma - Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, where is this "Death Valley"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about an hour or so if you travel in this direction by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten the both of you involved in our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let you go alone, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will rescue Professor Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to keep this a secret from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am one of The Three Musketeers of Doma, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you referring to the "Doma" in the cipher texts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those relics found underwater have something to do with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, or rather, the nameless Pharaoh, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I advise you not to involve yourself any further with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already turned your research lab into ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you can never stop us from researching the relics!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am not present, as long as those relics still exist in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are now free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have now finished my prior preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never forgive all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will defeat you, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow! Ouch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't help it, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should spare some thought for Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have informed the police about it after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca, where is Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They didn't think this through all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you noticed as well, Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two of us can never be "alone".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, leave Yugi to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of the professor and Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave Yugi in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where the heck did Haga and Ryuzaki go, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I must witness the match between Doma and Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn the secret to why Mai became even stronger than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're takin' this ta' get there 'fore he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! He's gonna surpass us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be there soon, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, we will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:22:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.01,0:22:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Doma's despicable methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi was made to proceed to Death Valley alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hopkins came back safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have no idea what kind of traps we will be facing in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy named Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cool and composed nature brings forth a certain danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of deck will he be choosing to Duel with?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yugi vs Rafael - The Impregnable Guardian Deck"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
